athu interface.

NOTE: 
* hiding the implementation details
[ ipo method laa ctrl+click panna abstract method kuu thaa pogum implementation 
method kuu pogathu ] 
1). oru abstract class laa 0 abstract methods irukalam but oru abstract method iruntha
kandipaa athu abstract class ah thaa irukanum.
2). best practice @override.
3). abstract class kuu object create panna mudiyathuu.

STORY::
1). nama grand father 3 rule podraru 10, 12 and college complete(pass) panniruthaa land ah 
own pannikelam nuu oru letter pottuttu death agirathu.
2). yenga father 10, 12 pass but college in-complete(fail) so land ah own panna mudiyathu
3). naan 10, 12 and college pass aguren so land ah own panniren(java laa land thaa object)
[ method kuu implementation pannathaa oru abstract method 
class kuu object create panna mudiyathu ]


DEFINTION::

** If a class is having, an unimplemented method, then the
method SHOULD BE declared abstract.
** If a class is having one abstract method then it SHOULD be declared Abstract
** It may or may not have implementation methods
** A class can be declared abstract even if doesn't have abstract methods.
** Can we create object for abstract class?
 --> N0000000000000.
** If a child does not implement all the abstract methods of parent class, 
then the child class must need to be declared abstract as well




